By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"部份同意  熱門完全冇818"},{"pid":"8e172a178553975256a5f87add2a0ddec92a49c6","tid":1462733,"uid":294562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"谷！"},{"pid":"308c70080416b594013fa9dbb3223aa69e7457fd","tid":1462733,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"塞機場算係升級 deadline完先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d8e1ddbc8d0b979a495562894260b5b7269c0c","tid":1462733,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308c70080416b594013fa9dbb3223aa69e7457fd","tid":1462733,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"塞機場算係升級 deadline完先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"利申唔支持犯法"},{"pid":"569a8f0d2abf9235eb238fcb8b24b0f6b2f7f9de","tid":1462733,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"借post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 談社運正當性 ] 塞鐵阻人返工可以係因為依個香港佢地有份；亦解釋到點解唔好塞離境旅客~</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿我唔係講策略/效果既問題。<br />\n<br />\n無疑塞鐵/罷工會惹人反感，唔應該日日做。<br />\n<br />\n但亦無可否認既，就係依類不合作運動係有佢既道德正當性係入面，因為返工既人多數都係香港社會既一份子，而佢地係有責任去維護香港人既人權自由；所以你阻佢，就算對社運進程無好處都好，你都係出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相對地，離境旅客有好多都唔係香港既持份者，基本上佢地係無任何責任為我地既人權自由付出任何代價；最簡單既理解方法，就係我相信你自己都唔會認為自己對其他國家既人權自由有絕對既責任，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n所以，離境旅客係搞不得。<br />\n<br />\n但，我地有權去機場、有權係唔阻其他旅客既情況下坐地下，所以靠人多去令機場function唔到，責任就唔係我地度，剛剛星期一既塞爆機場亦係絕對無問題。"},{"pid":"f3ddb808692e58e00ef4925a65d48906c9e2a830","tid":1462733,"uid":209032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45c62ed5fb9dd9dede863faa6d34e06032555230","tid":1462733,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b7937d7e5da15a42b5adc3f61907445e18b50ca","tid":1462733,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"集中火力818！大力推818"},{"pid":"3e9d5fe13ba251ddac8198cd5838e809f9ccf8d5","tid":1462733,"uid":9583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6q9cFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6q9cFE.jpg&h=d517e575&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}